snippet.title: Sea of Solitude Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Dare to look at what lies beneath the surface. Join Kay – a young woman who is struggling with her inner demons – as she navigates the darkness that surrounds her. Explore a flooded city by boat and on foot, meet fantastical monsters, and discover what it truly means to be human.

Sea of Solitude is available now on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and Origin on PC: http://x.ea.com/58910.
